        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "\"See, this way,\" said the young instructor, and he slipped a short fuse into the tube and fastened the end with paper and a piece of twine.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
