        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "\"What made you think of them, Rob?\" asked one of the boys, looking admiringly at the lad of fourteen who had just spoken.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
