        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "\"I knew something had to be done,\" said Robert, \"as soon as I heard they weren't going to let us burn any candles to morrow night 'cause candles are so scarce.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
