        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "It was not long after, however, that Robert set himself to work out another problem.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "The Fultons lived near the Conestoga, and Robert and his younger brothers were very fond of fishing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "All they had to fish from was a light raft which they had built the summer before, and this cumbersome craft they had to pole from place to place.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "It was an exciting moment when Robert laid hands on the crank and started the two wheels.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000018_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000018_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "It was a proud moment for the young inventor.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000018_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000018_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "As they went down the river and passed people on the banks, he could not help laughing as he saw the surprise on their faces.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "The Lancaster schoolmaster heard of the boat, and said to a friend: \"Take my word for it, the world's going to hear from Rob Fulton some of these days.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000021_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000021_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "And he doesn't know what it means to be discouraged.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000021_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000021_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "'No, sir,' says Robert to me, 'I don't think so.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000023_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000023_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "Usually, however, when he was not inventing he was learning how to paint, and he had a number of teachers, one of whom was the famous Major Andre.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "A great deal of powder was stored in the town, and rifles, blankets, and clothing were manufactured there in large quantities.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000025_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000025_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "Andre was a very amiable young man, and took a great liking to the boy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000026_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000026_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "The Revolution had made it very difficult to obtain painting materials from abroad, and almost all the paints the boys used were home-made.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_294520_000027_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/294520/7892_294520_000027_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "But \"Quicksilver Bob\" was allowed to come and go as he would.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_295954_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/295954/7892_295954_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "There was a man who was very poor, but so well supplied with children that he was utterly unable to maintain them, and one morning more than once prepared to kill them, in order not to see their misery in dying of hunger, but his wife prevented him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_295954_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/295954/7892_295954_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "When there, he found the stream, went on and on alongside of it, till he came to the fountain head.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_295954_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/295954/7892_295954_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "Having looked about him to see where the damsel was, he espied her above a piece of water, like sunbeams threaded on a needle, and she was embroidering at a frame on stuff, the threads of which were young men's hair.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_295954_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/295954/7892_295954_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "As soon as he saw her, he made a reverence to her, and she stood on her feet and questioned him: \"Whence are you, unknown young man?\" But he held his tongue.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_295954_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/295954/7892_295954_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "She questioned him again: \"Who are you?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_295954_000007_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/295954/7892_295954_000007_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "Then she told him to sit down on her skirt.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_295954_000007_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/295954/7892_295954_000007_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "He did not wait for any more orders, but sat down, and she bent down her head to him, that he might examine it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_295954_000007_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/295954/7892_295954_000007_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "She noticed it, and ran at his heels full speed after him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7892_295954_000007_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7892/295954/7892_295954_000007_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7892",
        "content": "When he saw that she was about to overtake him, he threw the red kerchief, and she again occupied herself, admiring and gazing, till the poor man had again got a good way off.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
